    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/extras/3ad838b2644eb928c11d9e130451fdfc.avif?t=1707344348\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>Wake up in a war torn city, as you are hunted by formidable robotic invaders and desperate survivors alike. Take control of humanity’s last hope and navigate an decaying, apocalyptic city filled with powerful foes and dark secrets. Discover new abilities and test your skills in a challenging 2-D metroidvania adventure, all while learning the truth behind the mysterious Red Sun. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/extras/85f3df460cab48a4dc69cc9488dc57f5.poster.avif?t=1707344348\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/extras/85f3df460cab48a4dc69cc9488dc57f5.webm?t=1707344348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/extras/85f3df460cab48a4dc69cc9488dc57f5.mp4?t=1707344348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Mastery of the tools and abilities you’ve earned along the way are critical to survival. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/extras/c996ecc76ded62d296b62fc90c47eb5a.poster.avif?t=1707344348\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/extras/c996ecc76ded62d296b62fc90c47eb5a.webm?t=1707344348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/extras/c996ecc76ded62d296b62fc90c47eb5a.mp4?t=1707344348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Red Sun's enemies are intelligent and powerful, and the odds are often stacked against the player. A combination of stealth, evasion, and a little bit of brute force are the key to success.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/extras/2247143385178d7b06b5b51525e50eb8.poster.avif?t=1707344348\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/extras/2247143385178d7b06b5b51525e50eb8.webm?t=1707344348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392330/extras/2247143385178d7b06b5b51525e50eb8.mp4?t=1707344348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Several factions vie for control over the remnants of the destroyed city and its resources. Some are friends, many are foes. But it must be remembered that the enemy of your enemy might prove useful, if only for a few moments.",
